ges/dw/20260430/1126496227437842432965714.jpeg/DjgWXGyLWljT9YWjcxSvoajGrq-4Yhl-COxHdyHsR3c\" alt=\"衞生署今日早上約10時在金鐘海富中心一帶派傳單宣傳。（黃寶瑩攝）\"><figcaption>衞生署今日早上約10時在金鐘海富中心一帶派傳單宣傳。（黃寶瑩攝）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-30T11:45:37.237708+00:00","quality":{"score":3,"chars":1411,"images":21,"source":"HK01 社會","fallback":"none"}}